@page "/about"

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="fs-1 fw-bold">About the Small Talk Chatbot</h1>
        <p class="fs-5 text-muted">Engaging conversations powered by machine learning</p>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="fs-3">🗣️ Purpose</h2>
        <p>
            This chatbot is designed to bring casual conversation into your web application. Whether it’s witty remarks, helpful tips, or natural replies to everyday queries, the bot delivers lighthearted, context-aware interactions tailored for real-world usability.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="fs-3">⚙️ Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Small talk detection using ML.NET classification models</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Natural language interaction with dynamic response rendering</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Razor-based input</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Expressive chatbot persona with personality-rich replies</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="fs-3">🛠️ Tech Stack</h2>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
            <thead class="table-light">
                <tr>
                    <th>Technology</th>
                    <th>Function</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Blazor</td>
                    <td>UI components and rendering logic</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>ASP.NET Core API</td>
                    <td>Message routing and backend processing</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>C#</td>
                    <td>Business logic and chatbot response framework</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="fs-3">🤖 Chatbot Persona</h2>
        <p>
            Friendly. Witty. Helpful. Your chatbot doesn’t just respond—it connects. The tone and replies are crafted to mirror human-like conversation while staying informative and engaging. It's like chatting with a thoughtful sidekick who knows a bit of everything.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="fs-3">🚀 Get Involved</h2>
        <p>
            Want to add sentiment analysis, fine-tune response patterns, or connect with Hugging Face datasets? This chatbot is ready for exploration, extension, and integration. Let your conversation interface evolve with your vision!
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
